item.title: Sample Article 2
item.description: Peter Griffin is the main character of the American animated sitcom Family Guy. He is voiced by the series’ creator, Seth MacFarlane, and first appeared on television, along with the rest of the Griffin family, in the 15-minute pilot pitch of Family Guy on December 20, 1998.
